remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="865e7-102">Los quiebres de escala son discontinuidades intencionadas en el eje y que se usan con mayor frecuencia para redistribuir los puntos de datos de una serie en un gráfico.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-102">Scale breaks are intentional discontinuities on the Y-axis that are most often used to redistribute the data points in a series on a chart.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-103">Esta característica mejora la legibilidad cuando existen grandes diferencias entre los valores máximo y mínimo de los datos de una serie que se están trazando.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-103">This feature improves readability when there are large differences between the high and low values of the data in one series being plotted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-104">Los quiebres de escala no se dibujan las diferencias entre los datos de varias series.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-104">Scale breaks are not drawn for differences between data in multiple series.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="865e7-105">De forma predeterminada, se deshabilitan los quiebres de escala.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-105">By default, scale breaks are disabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-106">Puede habilitar quiebres de escala en el eje y estableciendo el <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.Enabled%2A> propiedad `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-106">You can enable scale breaks on the Y-axis by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.Enabled%2A> property to `true`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-107">Para cambiar la cantidad de espacio vertical del quiebre de escala, puede especificar un <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.Spacing%2A> valor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-107">To change the amount of vertical space of the scale break, you can specify a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.Spacing%2A> value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-108">Esto se calcula como un porcentaje de la escala del eje y.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-108">This is calculated as a percentage of the Y-axis scale.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="865e7-109">Debe existir una separación suficiente entre los intervalos de puntos de datos de una única serie para dibujar un quiebre de escala.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-109">You must have sufficient separation between ranges of data points in a single series to draw a scale break.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-110">De forma predeterminada, un quiebre de escala se puede agregar solo si hay una separación entre los intervalos de datos de al menos el 25% del gráfico.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-110">By default, a scale break can be added only if there is a separation between the data ranges of at least 25% of the chart.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-111">Si habilita un quiebre de escala pero no aparece, aunque hay una distancia suficiente entre los intervalos de datos, puede establecer el <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.CollapsibleSpaceThreshold%2A> propiedad en un valor menor que 25.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-111">If you enable a scale break but it does not appear, even though there is sufficient distance between the data ranges, you can set the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.CollapsibleSpaceThreshold%2A> property to a value less than 25.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="865e7-112">Los gráficos admiten hasta cinco quiebres de escala por gráfico; Sin embargo, el gráfico puede resultar ilegible si muestra más de un quiebre de escala.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-112">Charts support up to five scale breaks per chart; however, the chart can become unreadable if you display more than one scale break.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-113">Si tiene más de dos intervalos de datos, considere la posibilidad de usar un método diferente para mostrar estos datos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-113">If you have more than two data ranges, consider using a different method for displaying this data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-114">Use la <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.MaxNumberOfBreaks%2A> propiedad para reducir el número de quiebres de escala que se pueden mostrar en el gráfico.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-114">Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.MaxNumberOfBreaks%2A> property to reduce the number of scale breaks that can be displayed on the chart.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="865e7-115">Cuando se utiliza un quiebre de escala, las etiquetas de eje y pueden sufrir un desplazamiento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-115">When a scale break is used, the Y-axis labels may become offset.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="865e7-116">Para deshabilitar el desplazamiento de la etiqueta, establezca el <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.IsStaggered%2A> propiedad `false`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-116">To disable the label offset, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.IsStaggered%2A> property to `false`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="865e7-117">No se admiten los quiebres de escala en cualquiera de las condiciones siguientes:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-117">Scale breaks are not supported under any of the following conditions:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="865e7-118">Se utiliza circulares, de anillos, embudo, pirámide, radial o cualquier tipo de gráfico apilado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-118">Pie, doughnut, funnel, pyramid, radial or any stacked chart types are used.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="865e7-119">Intervalos personalizados para las etiquetas, marcas de graduación o líneas de cuadrícula están habilitadas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-119">Custom intervals for labels, tick marks or grid lines are enabled.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="865e7-120">Se establece el valor mínimo o máximo para el eje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-120">The minimum or maximum value for the axis is set.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="865e7-121">Se usan etiquetas personalizadas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-121">Custom labels are used.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="865e7-122">Se especifica un eje y logarítmico.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-122">A logarithmic Y-axis is specified.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="865e7-123">Vistas de eje en el eje y, que incluyen el desplazamiento y zoom, se usan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-123">Axis views on the Y-axis, which include scrolling and zooming, are used.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="865e7-124">Se utilizan gráficos 3D.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-124">3-D charts are used.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="865e7-125">En el ejemplo de código siguiente se muestra cómo habilitar y personalizar un quiebre de escala tras el <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control se ha agregado a la superficie de diseño.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="865e7-125">The following code example demonstrates how to enable and customize a scale break after the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control has been added to the design surface.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Imports System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
Private Function AddChartData()   
  
    chart1.Series("Default").Points.Add(New DataPoint(1, 2))   
    chart1.Series("Default").Points.Add(New DataPoint(2, 4))   
    chart1.Series("Default").Points.Add(New DataPoint(3, 400000))   
    chart1.Series("Default").Points.Add(New DataPoint(4, 3))   
  
End Sub  
  
Private Function AddScaleBreaks()  
  
   ' Enable scale breaks.  
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.Enabled = True   
  
   ' Show scale break if more than 25% of the chart is empty space.       
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.CollapsibleSpaceThreshold = 25   
  
   ' Set the line width of the scale break.      
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.LineWidth = 2   
  
   ' Set the color of the scale break.   
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.LineColor = Color.Red   
  
   ' If all data points are significantly far from zero, the chart will calculate the scale minimum value.   
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.StartFromZero = StartFromZero.Auto  
  
   ' Set the spacing gap between the lines of the scale break (as a percentage of the Y-axis).  
   chart1.ChartAreas["Default"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.Spacing = 2;  
  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
using System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
private void AddChartData()  
{  
   chart1.Series["Series1"].Points.Add(new DataPoint(1, 2));  
   chart1.Series["Series1"].Points.Add(new DataPoint(2, 4));  
   chart1.Series["Series1"].Points.Add(new DataPoint(3, 400000));  
   chart1.Series["Series1"].Points.Add(new DataPoint(4, 3));  
}  
  
private void AddScaleBreaks()  
{  
   // Enable scale breaks.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.Enabled = true;  
  
   // Show scale break if more than 25% of the chart is empty space.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.CollapsibleSpaceThreshold = 25;  
  
   // Set the line width of the scale break.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.LineWidth = 2;  
  
   // Set the color of the scale break.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.LineColor = Color.Red;  
  
   // If all data points are significantly far from zero, the chart will calculate the scale minimum value.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.StartFromZero = StartFromZero.Auto;  
  
   // Set the spacing gap between the lines of the scale break (as a percentage of the Y-axis).  
    chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.Spacing = 2;  
}  
```

  
  
